com.absio.container

Class Container

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.absio.container.Container

  • public class Container
extends Object
    This is the decrypted version of a SecuredContainer. It has the content, header and metadata. The content and header are not encrypted.

        public Container(Metadata metadata,

        Create a container with the given metadata, content and header.

        NOTE: the metadata must be defined or a IllegalArgumentException will be thrown

        Parameters:
        metadata - the metadata for the container
        content - the content for the container
        header - the header for the container
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - thrown if the metadata is null
